  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If <span class=\"italic \">x</span> is a solution to the given equation, which of the following is a possible value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x plus 5\"></span> ?</p>\n",
